        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
