            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has browned, add the <strong>diced</strong> <strong>onion</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>cumin seeds</strong>, <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 6-7 min further or until the onion has started to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
