    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the onion is softening, dissolve your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>and a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>in 350ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [500ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[650ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your<strong> spicy stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
