    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse your <strong>butter beans</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>drained butter beans</strong>, <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and <strong>spicy stock </strong>to the pot and cook for 6-8 min or until the soup has thickened slightly and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>warming Mexican-style chicken soup</strong></p>",
