      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>warming</strong> <strong>Mexican-style chicken soup</strong> in bowls and dollop over your <strong>soured cream</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>tortilla chips </strong>to the side, ready for dipping</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
